msg":"見到義士俾人拉好心up"},{"pid":"8231ec23b8b68c3354f7f97630af78a7a801adf7","tid":1386990,"uid":88141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:49:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d99d096c724ed13f53eaa15a42b76dd200d3cd6e","tid":1386990,"uid":88167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:31:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"24d0739053073ba1e0bd00fe6ebf71d962be3962","tid":1386990,"uid":262125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0970cc0812e75f4d87babce0ed426faed188d54b","tid":1386990,"uid":88167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:35:13.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咪再打陣地戰，打遊擊</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\nBe Water唔係講緊「散水」果個water，係講緊水一樣既<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">流動性</span></span></strong>呀<br />\n728既慘況相信大家係有目共睹<br />\n點解唔打陣地戰:<br />\n<br />\n1. 有野好守就話打姐，但問題係守咩?守住條路又點?守到14年果陣咁守足咁多日又點?事實就係證明，<strong>塞死條路其實作用根本唔大</strong>，E家就係陷入左佔路-&gt;守-&gt;催淚彈+速龍+防暴-&gt;守唔住-&gt;被捕  咁樣既死循環<br />\n<br />\n2. 一定要承認裝備差距係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">太撚遠</span></strong>，就算有人full gear、好多人full gear，講裝備都係唔會夠班公安鬥(更何況佢地黎緊仲有水炮車，守條撚咩)。最直接講就係10 full gear夢遊者 vs 10 full gear 公安(10個廢柴防暴都好)，都係會輸，就算嬴，都只會慘勝，<strong>因為硬碰硬會有損傷係好正常兼合乎邏輯既事</strong>，所以先要盡量<strong>避免</strong>硬碰硬<br />\n <br />\n仲有D原因，但唔多講，最主要以上兩樣<br />\n咁跟住落黎應該點做?<br />\n<br />\n我覺得關鍵字係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Hit &amp; Run</span> </span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">現場傾目標-&gt;少人就遠攻、多人就圍攻-&gt;完成目標後即走，絕不可戀戰，有體力就潛伏等候重複以上行動既時機/ 無就即時走，換裝訓醒/交低裝比其他繼續發緊惡夢既人-&gt;視乎現場人數決定幾時撤退</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n至於點攻、咩方式攻，大把其他po講，不詳述<br />\n最後想講既只有一樣野<br />\n<br />\n有咩想做安心做，唔洗諗咩民意逆轉，輿論野交比文宣組/冷氣軍師們去處理。無論你地做咩，都<strong>絕對唔會</strong>有同路人割席<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">真‧Be Water, My friend</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:32:06.000Z","msg":"少一個都太多 :("},{"pid":"1ef8a3e8e8bfcec8995db6de92e376d2872a196e","tid":1386990,"uid":24265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:34:27.000Z","msg":"Hit and run<br />\n<br />\n每人請佢飲枝可樂都仆街啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一人一可樂 啤酒</span>"},{"pid":"af10087c788a05b601ebcc0ebd160cc09b77d94e","tid":1386990,"uid":150907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:36:02.000Z","msg":"真係唔好再大量送頭<br />\n一聽見呢啲消息<br />\n和理非就退無士氣<br />\n覺得唔好搞勒再搞就推啲後生仔去死乜乜乜<br />\n我哋要keep住成功撚狗保持士氣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f91f4742df0ef6b6e701b4905479ade3b49988a","tid":1386990,"uid":88167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ef8a3e8e8bfcec8995db6de92e376d2872a196e","tid":1386990,"uid":24265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:34:27.000Z","msg":"Hit and run<br />\n<br />\n每人請佢飲枝可樂都仆街啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一人一可樂 啤酒</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:43:26.000Z","msg":"極端d講，hit唔hit得中都唔係重點<br />\n例如大家睇下外國示威片就知，十枝雞尾酒，其實可能得2枝係中，其他好多都跌落地<br />\n但當e個過程不斷重複，每十枝有兩枝中，班公安要全程集中精神提防+跑住追人，消耗就絕對會更大"},{"pid":"2165670b85e6944d17580e250b166e9698fdbc94","tid":1386990,"uid":262890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:51:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e823ac160163060999a3b9ffc4e7c3d098212b55","tid":1386990,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:58:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}